Package org.cst8288Lab2.parser

Class CSVParser

java.lang.Object
org.cst8288Lab2.parser.CSVParser
public class CSVParser extends Object
This Singleton class contains methods that will parse a row of a CSV file and split the row. The split row is then mapped to the corresponding column names and returned in a Map.
Version:
Java 17
Author:
Dan Blais
